  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2f89e37e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FcAd6ObKOzECfJpFzZYpTSg5GcZgwXm6d5RB7MoWXSEk7nMzJ7I2whPD2BTPGCd3Pe1Pkzgrzg6ITtro1BGu3IA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">奇舞推荐</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\" style=\"outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:18px;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(61, 167, 66);font-size: 12px;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 28.4444px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span></h2>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;background-position:0% 0%;background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-clip:border-box;word-break:break-word;width:auto;font-family:Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.03em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&amp;mid=2247557443&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4dd073d6e780f146ba10237b403ad754&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">从极速复制“死了么”APP，看AI编程时代的技术选型</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过复刻“死了么”APP，展示如何用AI工具+Qoder+Supabase快速实现全栈开发，强调声明式技术栈、自动化服务和AI友好架构在MVP落地中的关键作用。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&amp;mid=2247557538&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2ae6648085081892642b6bde75b5cc51&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">极速开发出一个高质量 Claude Agent Skills 最佳实践</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">介绍Claude Skills的核心机制与开发流程，提出“让AI写Skill”的理念，强调上下文工程、渐进式披露和复利思维，帮助开发者高效构建可复用的AI能力模块。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MzYzMjE0MQ==&amp;mid=2247517928&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=67a360ce0119faa8d37d81678eb376a5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">用第一性原理拆解 Agentic Coding：从理论到实操</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从LLM本质出发，系统解析Agentic Coding的核心机制、上下文限制与最佳实践，提出“短对话优于长对话”“复利工程”等原则，指导开发者成为AI的“驾驭者”。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术实践</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:18px;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(61, 167, 66);font-size: 12px;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 28.4444px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span></h2>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;background-position:0% 0%;background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-clip:border-box;word-break:break-word;width:auto;font-family:Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.03em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODYwMjI2MA==&amp;mid=2649798388&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e0312f3b4b60675a40411281e86c4469&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">认知重建：Speckit 用了三个月，我放弃了——走出工具很强但用不好的困境</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者从Speckit的规范驱动困境出发，转向AI工程化路径，提出“上下文完整性+知识复利”新范式，构建Agent+Skill架构，实现边际成本递减与经验持续沉淀。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxOTY5MDMxNA==&amp;mid=2455765731&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f302b5e831ce99b22cb62c1efa30bd49&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">AI 实践：Code Insight 代码搜索定位的实践分享</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">介绍基于RAG与AST的代码索引系统，支持语义搜索、调用链分析与测试生成，结合AI模型提升问答精准度与问题定位效率，实现低成本、高召回的智能代码理解平台。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">拓展边界</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-style=\"outline: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-family:-apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:25.6px;text-align:center;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 18px; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:18px;\"><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 218, 81); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span><span data-style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 28.4444px; white-space-collapse: preserve; visibility: visible;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-size:12px;font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:28.4444px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(61, 167, 66);font-size: 12px;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 28.4444px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">■</span></span></span></h2>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.03em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&amp;mid=2247693989&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=aab8bb5f9fd0084532812ccd50ca1907&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">提示词技巧分享：一劳永逸版！</a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供一套通用提示词模板，支持文生图、图生文、视频脚本等场景，强调“让AI先思考再输出”，通过结构化提示提升生成质量与可控性，适合创作者反复使用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1MzE2NzIzMg==&amp;mid=2247501669&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=930ebe202cd65599b5dbf4c94cc1de19&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">从零开始的大模型之旅｜解码大模型：开篇&amp;技术篇1.1—基础架构概念</a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">系统梳理大模型核心技术概念，涵盖Transformer、预训练、MoE、涌现能力等，结合生活化类比与数学原理，帮助读者构建从架构到生态的完整认知体系。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(145, 109, 213);text-decoration: none;border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(200, 182, 226);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&amp;mid=2247542504&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e615d0d204429162ed96fd7f71f870c8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">得物App智能巡检技术的探索与实践</a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 1em 0px;line-height: 1.75;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于视觉语言模型构建App智能巡检系统，支持布局错乱、视觉异常、多页一致性等问题检测，结合AI操作与真机调度，实现80%+识别准确率，显著提升测试效率。</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "奇舞周刊第 579 期精选多篇 AI 编程与大模型技术文章，涵盖 AI 辅助开发实践、Agentic Coding 理论、代码搜索及 App 巡检等，展示 AI 如何赋能前端开发。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "奇舞周刊第 579 期精选多篇 AI 编程与大模型技术文章，涵盖 AI 辅助开发实践、Agentic Coding 理论、代码搜索及 App 巡检等，展示 AI 如何赋能前端开发。",
  "summary": "本文是奇舞周刊第 579 期的技术内容精选合集，汇集了多篇关于 AI 编程、大模型技术、以及前端 AI 应用的深度文章。内容涵盖了如何利用 AI 工具实现全栈 APP 快速开发、Claude Agent Skills 的最佳实践、Agentic Coding 的理论与实操、基于 RAG 和 AST 的 AI 代码搜索，以及大模型基础架构概念解析和基于视觉语言模型的 App 智能巡检等。这些文章共同呈现了 AI 时代下，开发者如何借助 AI 提升开发效率、优化工作流，并应对技术挑战的多元视角和实践经验，旨在帮助读者把握 AI 前沿技术，赋能实际开发。",
